    "title": "An Italian magazine cover featuring a photograph of an armed Israeli settler gri...",
    "description": "An Italian magazine cover featuring a photograph of an armed Israeli settler grinning at a distressed Palestinian woman under the title \u201cThe Abuse\u201d has caused a diplomatic backlash from Israel. The magazine issue explores the expansion of settlements and settler violence in the occupied West Bank.",
    "link": "https://www.facebook.com/saerzulkarnain/posts/pfbid0dQg3aQFHK2kH5r3kJjVib1c68U8qtLxU8LaUXPPV99iF1krqPNtsv1LRaLXyuZbnl",
    "guid": "https://www.facebook.com/saerzulkarnain/posts/pfbid0dQg3aQFHK2kH5r3kJjVib1c68U8qtLxU8LaUXPPV99iF1krqPNtsv1LRaLXyuZbnl",
